== 製作 ==
=== 開發 ===
2013年8月19日，ABC向Shondaland製作公司購買了原創故事，並由[[珊達·萊梅斯|珊達·萊梅斯]]與{{link-en|貝西·碧兒絲|Betsy Beers}}擔任製作。試播集的腳本由《[[實習醫生_(電視劇)|實習醫生]]》製作人之一的[[彼得·諾沃克|彼得·諾沃克]]執筆。<ref name="Writer">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2013/08/abc-buys-legal-thriller-from-shondaland-greys-anatomy-writer-567157/|title=ABC Buys Legal Thriller From Shondaland & ‘Grey’s Anatomy’ Writer|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2013-08-19|accessdate=2014-05-05}}</ref>2013年12月19日，ABC宣布預訂試播集。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/sea-of-fire-shondalands-how-to-get-away-with-murder-get-abc-pilot-orders/|title='Sea Of Fire' & Shondaland's 'How To Get Away With Murder' Get ABC Pilot Orders|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2013-12-19|accessdate=2014-05-05|archive-date=2014-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140423072715/http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/sea-of-fire-shondalands-how-to-get-away-with-murder-get-abc-pilot-orders/|dead-url=no}}</ref>本劇試播集於[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]之[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的[[南加州大學|南加州大學]]；[[賓夕法尼亞州|賓夕法尼亞州]]的[[費城|費城]]、[[布林莫爾_(賓夕法尼亞州)|布林莫爾]]之[[布林莫爾學院|布林莫爾學院]]以及{{link-en|學院村 (賓夕法尼亞州)|Collegeville, Pennsylvania|學院村}}之{{link-en|烏爾西努學院|Ursinus College}}取景。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.ursinus.edu/2014/headlines/abc-films-new-pilot-on-ursinus-campus/|title=ABC Films New Pilot on Ursinus Campus|work=Ursinus College|last=|first=|date=2014-03-14|accessdate=2014-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140322214050/http://news.ursinus.edu/2014/headlines/abc-films-new-pilot-on-ursinus-campus/|archive-date=2014-03-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>並由{{link-en|麥克爾·奧佛|Michael Offer}}執導。<ref name="Director">{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/01/abc-drama-pilots-warriors-how-to-get-away-with-murder-find-directors/|title=ABC Drama Pilots 'Warriors' & 'How To Get Away With Murder' Find Directors|publisher=Deadline.com|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|date=2014-01-31|accessdate=2014-05-05|archive-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704124825/http://www.deadline.com/2014/01/abc-drama-pilots-warriors-how-to-get-away-with-murder-find-directors/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年5月8日，ABC將試播集訂於[[2014年－2015年美國電視網節目表|2014年－2015年電視季度]]首播。<ref>{{cite web|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/abc-picks-up-shonda-rhimes-how-to-get-away-with-murder-anthony-anderson-american-crime/|title=ABC New Series Pickups: 'Selfie', 'Forever', Galavant', 'Whispers', 'How To Get Away With Murder', 'American Crime', 'Black-ish', Jeff Lowell Comedy|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2014-05-08|accessdate=2014-05-12|archive-date=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713050410/http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/abc-picks-up-shonda-rhimes-how-to-get-away-with-murder-anthony-anderson-american-crime/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Cynthia Littleton|url=http://variety.com/2014/tv/news/abc-orders-viola-davis-drama-how-to-get-away-with-murder-1201176035/|title=ABC Orders ‘Marvel’s Agent Carter,’ 4 Other Dramas and 4 Comedies|publisher=綜藝雜誌|date=2014-05-08|accessdate=2014-05-05|archive-date=2015-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150831120708/http://variety.com/2014/tv/news/abc-orders-viola-davis-drama-how-to-get-away-with-murder-1201176035/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年7月，[[電視評論家協會|電視評論家協會]]新聞之旅報導本劇第一季將僅有15－16集左右，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/TVGuide/status/489095092636876801|title=#Scandal will do a full 22-episode season, while #HowToGetAwayWithMurder will only do 15 or 16 episodes #TCA14|publisher=[[電視指南_(雜誌)|電視指南]]|date=2014-07-15|accessdate=2014-07-16|archive-date=2015-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130224155/https://twitter.com/tvguide/status/489095092636876801|dead-url=no}}</ref>而其原因是因薇拉·戴維絲有其他戲約的關係。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/10/how-to-get-away-with-murder-blackish-full-season-1-orders-abc-848758/|title=‘How To Get Away With Murder’ & ‘Black-Ish': Full-Season Orders At ABC - Deadline|work=Deadline|date=2014-10-09|accessdate=20