== 評價 ==
[[File:Viola_Davis_(cropped).jpg|thumb]]擔綱主要角色安娜莉絲·基汀，並榮獲[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]及[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]]]
《逍遙法外》首播後廣受好評，尤其是女主角[[維奧拉·戴維斯|薇拉·戴維絲]]的演技，更是獲得一致盛讚。在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]整合的評論中，第1季獲得85%新鮮度、7.13/10分（53位評論家），評論家共識：「《逍遙法外》雖然概念非新意，但卻帶來驚險的戲劇性轉折與迷人的領導優勢。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/how-to-get-away-with-murder/|title=How to Get Away With Murder: Season 1 (2014)|publisher=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]|accessdate=2014-10-02|archive-date=2015-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928133354/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/how-to-get-away-with-murder/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]整合的評論中，第1季由獲得68分（滿分100分；30位評論家），屬於普遍的好評。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/how-to-get-away-with-murder|title=How to Get Away With Murder : Season 1|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2014-10-02|archive-date=2015-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418034925/http://www.metacritic.com/tv/how-to-get-away-with-murder|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]的瑪麗·麥克納馬拉（{{lang|en|Mary McNamara}}）與[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]的梅麗莎·馬爾斯（{{lang|en|Melissa Maerz}}）都給予戴維絲細膩的演技極高的評價。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/la-et-st-how-to-get-away-with-murder-review-20140925-column.html|title='How to Get Away With Murder' keeps spotlight on Viola Davis|publisher=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|accessdate=2016|archive-date=2017-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171214025435/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/la-et-st-how-to-get-away-with-murder-review-20140925-column.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2014/10/15/how-get-away-murder|title=How to Get Away With Murder|publisher=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]|accessdate=2016|archive-date=2016-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219202422/http://www.ew.com/article/2014/10/15/how-get-away-murder|dead-url=no}}</ref>

第2季評價更勝第1季，於爛番茄整合的評論中，第2季獲得94%新鮮度、8.21/10分（87位評論家），評論家共識：「本季發展更強烈的敘事，《逍遙法外》扔出更難以置信的衝擊與更高的驚險並加以混合，為上癮之火增添瘋狂的燃料。」<ref name="Rotten Tomato S2">{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/how-to-get-away-with-murder/s02/|title=How to Get Away With Murder: Season 2 (2015)|publisher=爛番茄|accessdate= 2015-11-09}}</ref>第3季獲得90%新鮮度、7.52/10分（30位評論家）。<ref name="Rotten Tomato S3">{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/how-to-get-away-with-murder/s03/|title=How to Get Away With Murder: Season 3 (2016)|publisher=爛番茄|accessdate=2017-03-02}}</ref>第4季獲得100%新鮮度、7.90/10分（8位評論家）。<ref name="Rotten Tomato S4">{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/how-to-get-away-with-murder/s04/|title=How to Get Away With Murder: Season 4 (2017)|publisher=爛番茄|accessdate=2017-10-29}}</ref>

